author: danj
msg: Modified FilterFactory implementation so that people can add 'handlers' for custom filter types. I made three
handlers for the spec-defined filter types.
I also added a FilterSerializer and added it to the registry in SimpleNP.initialize() so that people can
modify the filter property using WSRP SetRP.
